<P>THE <HI>POLITICAL</HI> CENSOR, OR MONTHLY REVIEW OF THE <HI>Mo&s;t intere&s;ting Political Occurrences,</HI> RELATIVE TO <HI>THE UNITED STATES</HI> OF <HI>AMERICA.</HI></P>
