Sitgreaves, Jeremiah Smith, N. Smith, I&s;aac Smith,</HI> W. Smith, <HI>Swift, Thatcher, Thomas, Thomp&s;on, Tracey, Van Allen, Wad&s;worth, Williams.</HI> 37.</P>
