<P><PB N="169" REF="030221_0101_0FE529D94AF32D48">N. B. This Cen&s;or, from a de&s;ire of in&s;erting two of the Speeches on the call for papers, has been &s;welled to an unu&s;ual bulk; but, as the introduction to the work promi&s;es that no augmentation of price &s;hall take place, that pro|mi&s;e will be adhered to. Debates, however, cannot in future be admitted: want of room, from a crowd of other matter, will oblige the Editor to confine him&s;elf to remarks on them.</P>
